title: TANTALIZING TUNA & CHICKEN
descriptions: Aatas Cat canned food is a great way to introduce variety to your cat’s diet, in addition to providing an alternate source of water for healthy hydration!
Savor the delectable freshness of Tuna, caught in an environmental-friendly way, and topped with shreds of slow-cooked Chicken.
Aatas Cat Tantalizing Tuna series is a complementary pet food for adult cats. Feed alongside Aatas Cat Dry Food, for a complete and balanced diet.
key_benefits: These tasty shreds of Tantalizing Tuna & Chicken in delicious savory aspic include natural, wholesome ingredients free from grains, artificial colors, flavors and preservatives.
All of Aatas Cat food cans are absolutely free from any intended use of BPA.
ingredients: Gelling agents (Seaweed, Cassia Gum, Guar Gum, Locust Bean Gum, Potassium Chloride & Carbonates)
